        <p>Felipe M. Affonso is an Assistant Professor of Marketing at Oklahoma State University. He received his Ph.D. in Marketing from the University of Florida. His research focuses on consumer judgment and decision-making, consumer inference-making, human-AI interaction and technology, and health, environment, and policy. His work has been published in leading marketing journals, including the <em>Journal of Consumer Research</em>, <em>Journal of Marketing</em>, and <em>Journal of Consumer Psychology</em>.</p>
